# Dev-root standards repo.
# This repo version-controls only the COMPANY-WIDE standards that live at the dev root
# (root CLAUDE.md + docs/). Each tool subproject (siamhan_crm, gsa01-*, gsa02/03, …)
# has its own git repo and lifecycle, so we ignore all top-level directories and then
# re-include just docs/.
/*/
!docs/
!docs/**

.DS_Store
*.log
